metadata.description:
EDITION 1 OF 1

Title: Precognitive Dreams - Painting The Future  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2022


"Precognitive Dreams - Painting The Future" is about an Artificial Intelligence machine that predicts the future through their dreams. Godwits creates a collection of 200 unique dreams on a digital canvas to bring the first "Black Label" signed collection. Imagine your future and create your own story from each painting.

These works are minted as authenticated tokens on Ethereum to show originality and to validate the creation date in case there are copycat works in the future.


Published By: Abstract Art Labs LLC  
Smart Contract By Manifold / Token Type: ERC-1155  
Artist Royalty: 8%
